e our results with comprehensive scaling\nrelations which avoid the need for full Fisher matrix calculations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Oct 2006 20:04:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Aug 2007 08:42:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-01-22"}
